mage" alt="Dua Lipa（左）和 Tame Impala 的 Kevin Parker（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/TameImpala-Kevin-Parker-praises-Dua-Lipa-Radical-Optimism.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/TameImpala-Kevin-Parker-praises-Dua-Lipa-Radical-Optimism-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/TameImpala-Kevin-Parker-praises-Dua-Lipa-Radical-Optimism-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/TameImpala-Kevin-Parker-praises-Dua-Lipa-Radical-Optimism-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/TameImpala-Kevin-Parker-praises-Dua-Lipa-Radical-Optimism-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/TameImpala-Kevin-Parker-praises-Dua-Lipa-Radical-Optimism-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-parker">凯文·帕克 (Kevin Parker)</a>在其新录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">《激进乐观》(Radical Optimism)</a>发行后称赞他的合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a>是“绝对武器”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">杜阿·利帕（Dua Lipa）——“激进乐观”评论：夏季但轻微的心理流行</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tame-impala">Tame Impala</a>主唱与歌手共同制作并共同创作了第三张唱片，即 2020 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/dua-lipa-future-nostalgia-album-review-2633945#:~:text=When%20she%20made%20this%20album,only%20for%20a%20little%20while.">《Future Nostalgia》</a>的后续唱片，该唱片已于今天（5 月 3 日）发行。他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/danny-l-harle">Danny L. Harle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tobias-jesso-jr">Tobias Jesso Jr.</a>和 Caroline Ailin 等人一起参与了这个包含 11 首曲目的项目。</p><p>今天下午，帕克在 Instagram 上写道：“祝这张令人兴奋的专辑发行日快乐，并祝贺这张绝对的武器本身。”</p><p>他继续说道：“我从来没有为自己在发布日所做的事情感到如此自豪。也向其他天才大喊一声<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 。非常感激能成为其中的一部分。你们听听……@dualipa。”</p><p>这位音乐家兼制作人附上了专辑封面以及他与利帕和同事在录音室里的一些幕后照片。你可以看看下面的帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6gNhGjSrJ0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 54